ocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b06ebf3a1d0a6af78f3af15e50d19f0222f745","tid":1814533,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe88069514283c28ce2940f20d79eafe0f23eac","tid":1814533,"uid":259493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:28:49.000Z","msg":"文宣組 /舉牌/噴字/國際戰線手足，請你們準備最新字句和圖片、 我們要務必要登上各地財經版頭條<br />\n我們要針對四大類人；律師、股東、基金持有人、當地選民<br />\n<br />\n1、美/歐/日律師們，你們發達了，即時告知客戶們，控告銀行或基金經理投資中國， 因為完全缺乏透明度， 黑箱作業根本長期損害投資者利益。<br />\n<br />\n2、擁有銀行股票的股東或基金持有人，必須要求銀行和基金經理對中國貸款極多擔保物/極高利息回報<br />\n<br />\n3、 債務堆積如山的中國就是龐氏計劃； 沒有新債支持、舊債就即時爆煲。各地選民請質問議員/總統候選人，為何仍投資邪惡又不能還款的中國<br />\n<br />\nTo save Hong Kong , Stop all loan to China！<br />\nLoan to China only after HK Referendum"},{"pid":"409de9bd8dc3bf57e18d16b73ce693dd0b5ea498","tid":1814533,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:29:16.000Z","msg":"突發！和勇全面退場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1814289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1814289</a>"},{"pid":"34f3799fe6bd5436aac20aba2a88b2d1a4493a0b","tid":1814533,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:34:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf4dc14d75ec4601691cc68a4532c0567f26305f","tid":1814533,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6a5824f3bd8de97e64a5a38a33af41d3395668","tid":1814533,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">捉鬼既從來都唔係同路人</span>"},{"pid":"7d990260c6af3ee92ad3fc07ea9315f3b581979d","tid":1814533,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef6a5824f3bd8de97e64a5a38a33af41d3395668","